Class InitialHandlerAndStorer

java.lang.Object
pl.sydygaliev.java_journey.model.InitialHandlerAndStorer
public class InitialHandlerAndStorer extends Object
This class is used to store data from the user and check validity. Controller isn't responsible for storing data that's why this class was implemented.
